ZH: 我们必须经受挑战才能成长。
EN: We must endure challenges in order to grow.

ZH: 他经受了许多痛苦，但他从中学到了很多东西。
EN: He endured a lot of pain, but he learned a lot from it.

ZH: 她的友谊经受住了时间的考验。
EN: Her friendship stood the test of time.

ZH: 这个国家经受了许多灾难，但它仍然存在。
EN: This country has endured many disasters, but it still exists.

ZH: 他经受了很多困难，但他从未放弃。
EN: He has endured a lot of hardships, but he never gave up.

ZH: 在这场战争中，我们的军队经受了很大的打击。
EN: Our army suffered a great deal in this war.

ZH: 这个家庭经受了严重的财务困难。
EN: This family has endured severe financial difficulties.

ZH: 学生们经受了艰苦的学习，最终获得了成功。
EN: Students endured tough studying and eventually achieved success.

ZH: 在这场危机中，我们必须经受住压力。
EN: In this crisis, we must withstand the pressure.

ZH: 这个城市经受了地震的袭击，但很快恢复了。
EN: This city endured the impact of the earthquake, but quickly recovered.

ZH: 她的表现经受了老板的严格审查。
EN: Her performance was under strict examination by the boss.

ZH: 这个项目经受了很多争议，但最终成功完成了。
EN: This project underwent a lot of controversy, but was eventually completed successfully.

ZH: 他经受了家庭分裂的痛苦。
EN: He suffered from the pain of a broken family.

ZH: 这种建筑材料能经受住火灾的考验。
EN: This building material can withstand the test of fire.

ZH: 我们的友谊经受了许多风浪，但却更加坚固。
EN: Our friendship has weathered many storms and become even stronger.

ZH: 这个团队经受了很多挑战，但他们团结一致取得了胜利。
EN: This team faced many challenges, but they united and achieved victory.

ZH: 这部小说描写了一个经受了重重困难的女主人公。
EN: This novel depicts a female protagonist who endured many difficulties.

